'''Gengi Tung''' was a member of the [[shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. After [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] began executing several ranking shapers over their inability to control the [[World Brain]] of [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]], Tung found himself [[Escalation|escalated]] to [[Master Shaper]].

The escalation came as a surprise to many other shapers&mdash;none more surprised than Tung himself. However, he refused to let anyone humiliate him, or be brought down by some ambitious [[Domain]]. As a result, Master Tung often accompanied [[Warrior caste|warriors]] into the field, searching for renegade [[Coruscanti/Legends|Coruscanti]], wielding a [[Tsaisi]] instead of the [[Finger-spear|whip sting]] so commonly found in [[shaper hand]]s. At all times, he was accompanied by [[Toi]] and [[Tixo]], his two pet [[umrach]]s.

